isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:432:"Recently, our very own Jayvie Canono created a new magazine theme for our StartBox Theme Framework. He wanted to put simplicity into setting up a &#8220;magazine style&#8221; theme on your website. Brochure; which is the name of the new theme &#8230; <a class="more-link" href="http://webdevstudios.com/2013/04/05/jayvie-canono-creates-a-new-magazine-theme-for-startbox-2/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Melissa Hoppe";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2430:"<p>Recently, our very own <a title="Jayvie Canono" href="http://webdevstudios.com/team/jayvie-canono/">Jayvie Canono </a>created a new magazine theme for our <a href="http://wpstartbox.com/">StartBox Theme Framework</a>. He wanted to put simplicity into setting up a &#8220;magazine style&#8221; theme on your website.</p>\n<p><a href="http://wpstartbox.com/themes/brochure/">Brochure</a>; which is the name of the new theme &#8211; was designed with &#8220;being different&#8221; in mind. You have many areas that you can place widgets in, so that you can easily customize your site to make it stand out from all the other news sites.</p>\n<p><a href="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/brochure.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-7326" alt="brochure" src="http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/brochure.png" width="654" height="145" /></a></p>\n<p>Jayvie created three different feels to this new theme. This is how he described them on the <a href="http://wpstartbox.com/2013/03/22/meet-brochure/">StartBox website blog</a>:</p>\n<blockquote><p>Visually, I made three different “looks”, all very different from each other in character. “Elegant” has a classic look that invokes the look and feel of old paper; “Modern,” whose name speaks for itself, and “Columbia,” a feminine—and rather daring—look dedicated to the classic personification of the United States.</p></blockquote>\n<p>It was also designed to work in tangent with all different types of layouts and adapts to the lot of them perfectly. Magazine themes almost always have slideshows. StartBox has a built in slideshow feature, which is extremely customizable &#8211; allowing you to make the slideshow as big or small as you want for your site. (How cool is that?!)</p>\n<p>Brochure is also responsive &#8211; allowing users to see your site in full action on tablets and smartphones! There&#8217;s a demo to see how awesomely responsive it is &#8211; <a href="http://www.responsinator.com/?url=http://demo.wpstartbox.com/?theme=brochure">Check it out!</a></p>\n<p>To view full details on Brochure; see the <a href="http://wpstartbox.com/2013/03/22/meet-brochure/">blog post</a> on <a href="http://wpstartbox.com/">StartBox&#8217;s website.</a></p>\n<a href="http://webdevstudios.com/2013/04/05/jayvie-canono-creates-a-new-magazine-theme-for-startbox-2/#gallery-7325-1-slideshow">Click to view slideshow.</a>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:99:"http://webdevstudios.com/2013/04/05/jayvie-canono-creates-a-new-magazine-theme-for-startbox-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6